{{> header title="SIM Swap in progress"}}

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Your mobile SIM swap is in progress</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Hi %%NAME%%,
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          A SIM swap has been submitted for your {{brand.displayName}} mobile number.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>{{brand.displayName}} mobile number:</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          %%MOBILE_NUMBER%%
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>What happens next</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>SIM swap in progress</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Your SIM swap should be completed within 15 minutes. Once complete, you’ll no longer have access to your old SIM.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Activate and set up your eSIM</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          If you weren’t able to activate and set up your eSIM through the app when you submitted your SIM swap, head to our %%SUPPORT_PAGE%% for everything you need to know about getting set up.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Need help?</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Give us a call on {{brand.support.phone}} – we’re available 24/7.
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px 60px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}};">
          Thanks,<br>
          Your {{brand.displayName}} Team
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

{{> footer}}
